{"tid":2207388,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共不認糧食危機　強逼農民砍樹種糧","createTime":"2020-09-18T06:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T11:05:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3dd829b8f39ae37f4a3dedc027af3c1c66f577","tid":2207388,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200918/AVRDMC5UTFGCLN4JPCNBLTSOSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200918%2FAVRDMC5UTFGCLN4JPCNBLTSOSA%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdTsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=ec373fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200918%2FAVRDMC5UTFGCLN4JPCNBLTSOSA%2F&h=cbc22d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200918/AVRDMC5UTFGCLN4JPCNBLTSOSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/6fe5368fly1gcy1dtdlytj20w01kw0wz-300x533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F6fe5368fly1gcy1dtdlytj20w01kw0wz-300x533.jpg&h=a70f8a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平罕見號召要制止中國餐飲浪費的現象，引發許多人猜測，中國正面臨迫在眉睫的糧食短缺。網媒《寒冬》報導，政府正在採用嚴厲的手段，逼各地農民種植糧食作物。<br />\n<br />\n網媒《寒冬》（Bitter Winter）報導， 4月山東省新泰市石萊鎮政府，要求各村今後5年內，不能種樹，只種糧食，已經種植的樹木，也要在限期內砍掉，以便種植糧食作物。之後，當地政府在未徵求村民同意情況下，派人將左家溝村新栽種的楊樹一夜間全部剪斷。村民向政府申訴，得到的回答是，「政府不讓栽樹，讓種糧食」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/Untitled-3-450x308.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FUntitled-3-450x308.gif&h=2219bfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一位村民說：「政府號召種糧食，因為國家的糧庫空了，中國現在又不能從美國進口糧食。」還有人表示：「他們夜裡偷偷就給毀了，政府起碼得通知我們一聲，被剪斷的樹，我們沒法賣，只能當柴燒。反正在中國遭殃的總是老百姓。」<br />\n<br />\n還有60多歲的村民說：「那些地痞拿著長木棍子，誰反抗就打誰，誰敢吱聲呀。這次砍樹政策是強制性的，沒有商量的餘地。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2015/10/1312240807392320-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2F1312240807392320-600x400.jpg&h=01534b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣東省廣州市政府則逼那些已無力務農的老年人，種植水稻。<br />\n<br />\n當地一村民表示：「政府發通知，5月1日起，所有水田要種稻穀，不可以種樹，否則就收回我們土地經營權。」<br />\n<br />\n在中國，農田歸集體所有，由國家控制，農民只有承包權和經營權。因此，政府現在以收回承包權和經營權，脅迫農民種植糧食作物。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市另一個村的農民，也被要求限期內把果樹與蔬菜剷毀，種上了稻穀。村民表示，政府沒有給任何賠償。「我家的荔枝樹很快就可以摘果了，卻被剷了，損失一萬多元人民幣（約43,063元台幣）。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指，中國經濟學家胡星斗認為，中國糧食產量不穩定，中國可能面臨被海外斷糧的風險。報導引述胡星斗接受《明報》訪問時表示，「恐怕中國未來還是需要依靠自給自足，提高自給率到90%、95%。」目前中國糧食自給率在80%左右，仍是全球最大糧食進口國。<br />\n<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"7ea64e2c8afe2ab8a486c5d0c2882b93375fc867","tid":2207388,"uid":99872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"仲有大把草"},{"pid":"5dd3729e31b182ed1bef9118edd63ddf9e27cb78","tid":2207388,"uid":39256,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"打風點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13508836e06fdce10ec48c542be20338315cfed","tid":2207388,"uid":330457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"仲有樹皮食 唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a974f2219dcaa2eec783b3c23c126303ade14ab4","tid":2207388,"uid":17765,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"話剷就剷 話種就種<br />\n玩緊真人版動物森友會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b9aff01f2618e2eda7bacec97c19cfc9b4d5fb","tid":2207388,"uid":54125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"糧未種起就樹皮都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de33f237b2ec063ba338be70591bf9059732934","tid":2207388,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"r